Class Identifiable

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReferenceId

    public class Identifiable
extends Hl7v2Based<ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.datatype.CX>
    Represents an ID.

    This class is derived from an HL7v2 CX data type. The XDS profile limits the data type to two of its components (CX.1 and CX.4).

    All members of this class are allowed to be null. When transforming to HL7 this indicates that the values are empty. Trailing empty values are removed from the HL7 string.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider, Dmytro Rud
